This is the PD version of the game "Alien Fish Finger".  This version
can be freely distributed.  It can be down loaded from a BBS, a CD
disk, a magazine cover disk, or given to by a friend.  But the
Copyright remains with the author.  I.E. You are NOT allowed to modify
any part of this program, or sell it for much of a profit.

INFORMATION: to Public Domain Libraries

If you would like to sell this game, please obey the following rules:-

   (1)  Charge no more than £1.25 (UK Sterling Pounds).
        This price includes disk, postage, packing and labour costs.
   (2)  Orders must be sent within 10 days of receiving order.
   (3)  Do not put any of your PD Libraries logos, icons or
        advertisements on to this disk, unless it is part of a
        collection, such as the Assassins, or Fresh Fish.

Thank you for taking note.


Game Info
~~~~~~~~~

"Alien Fish Finger" is a flip-screen platform shoot em' up game.  You
guide a little bloke, named Frank Finger around lots of levels blowing
the guts out of lots of Aliens.  It's as simple as that.

Sorry to say, but this game is shareware.  So, if you find your self
playing it a lot, then please register.  The shareware fee is only
£3.99 inc.P&P (UK Sterling Pounds).  Countries other than the U.K. can
register by sending cash for £5.00 (U.K. Sterling Pounds) 

In return you will receive the full version with all the levels, a
printed information sheet, including a printed disk label, and my
thanks.  Plus a free PD game too.


